<span class="line">    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>span<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>笔画粗细<span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>span<span class="token operator">&gt;</span></span>
